description: This stunning 2 bed + den / 2 bath condo with garage parking was built in 2023 & perfectly located in Southie’s East Side. Thoughtfully designed with a modern open floor plan, the chef’s kitchen is equipped with high-end Fisher & Paykel appliances & Calcatta quartz countertops/ island. The expansive living/ dining area is flooded with natural light from the oversized windows & is perfect for entertaining. Both bedrooms are generously sized, offering flexibility for a WFH setup. The primary suite features a  custom walk-in closet that leads to a beautiful en-suite bathroom with double vanities & glass-enclosed shower. The adjoining den makes for a great office/ extra storage space. Set within a professionally managed, elevator building with a common courtyard. All this, and just moments to Castle Island, M Street Beach/Park, Curley Community Center & the bars/ restaurants on E Broadway with easy access to the Seaport.
